      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Florence Healthcare a CTMS?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Florence Healthcare is primarily a document and workflow platform — an eISF, eTMF, and eConsent solution — not a full CTMS. It excels at site file organization, remote monitoring access for sponsors, and informed consent digitization. It does not natively replace functions like visit scheduling, protocol deviation tracking, IRB submission tracking, monitoring visit management, or invoice management that a CTMS like Nexrial covers as core features."
      }
